    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;OAuth 2.0 public clients utilizing the Authorization Code Grant are susceptible to the authorization code interception attack.  This specification describes the attack as well as a technique to mitigate against the threat through the use of Proof Key for Code Exchange (PKCE, pronounced "pixy").&lt;/p&gt;</t>
